sequenceDiagram
accTitle: Mermaid central connections
accDescr {
Demonstrates Mermaid central connections mapped onto sequencer endpoint anchors.
From the project root, regenerate this Mermaid transform and SVG with:
node sequencer.js --mermaid -i test/mermaid-features/16-central-connections/input.mmd -o -f -t test/mermaid-features/16-central-connections
}
participant Caller
participant Service
