Caller()->>Service: Source central sync [Mermaid: Caller()->>Service: Source central sync]
Service-->>()Caller: Target central return [Mermaid: Service-->()Caller: Target central return]
Caller()->>()DB: Both central sync [Mermaid: Caller()->>()DB: Both central sync]
DB()-)Service: Source central async [Mermaid: DB()-)Service: Source central async]
